            <div type="translation">
                <p> P(ublius) Oppi[us, son of...],
 	of (the tribe of) Camilia,
	...cio, of Ravenna,
	soldier of the Legio V
	Macedonica, (of the rank of) optio,
	lived
	30 years, served in the army nine years
 	(and) is buried here.
	(His) heir made (this tombstone). 
